snippet.title: Two Sides Podcast
snippet.description:
Our Names our Kaitlyn and Sam

We have opened this channel for us the creators to you the viewer to have a podcast where we can be vocal on topics we are passionate about  These topics can range from anything trendy to something serious in news today that we should discuss and perhaps not be overlooked.

as the viewers/listeners of our podcast, we encourage you to be open with us and share  your views 

we listen to all sides!!
